   Hill delayed packing the lobsters for their trip until the last
possible minute. ``Believe it or not, I'm still getting people
coming by the window to look at 'em,'' he said <DATE>Monday</DATE>.
   Pity <ORGANIZATION>Not Cruelty Inc.</ORGANIZATION>, a small animal rights group, made
